maml:description.maml:para: Add hostnames to a property's hostname bucket.

Adds hostnames to a property's hostname bucket. Each Hostname object you provide must be made up of a certProvisioningType, cnameFrom (the hostname itself), cnameType (always EDGE_HOSTNAME), and edgeHostnameId.
